Wave - Class in com.vtuberrush.src.waves
A wave is an integer array list whose elements are the enemy types.
Waves are constructed in the WaveManager and are used for spawning defined enemy types in short intervals when a new wave is started in the game.
Wave(ArrayList<Integer>) - Constructor for class com.vtuberrush.src.waves.Wave
Creates a new wave using the passed integers as the enemy types.
WaveManager - Class in com.vtuberrush.src.managers
Facilitates the spawning of waves or groups of enemies in set intervals.
WaveManager(Playing) - Constructor for class com.vtuberrush.src.managers.WaveManager
Initializes and creates a list of waves for the player to defend against.
